.) held at Jaat & Punjabi Dharam Shala, Palwal Haryana and secured 2<sup>nd</sup> position in the above 25 years age category.\n# 4<sup>th</sup> North East India Yoga Physique Samrat & Samragni Championship 2003 Organised by Rising Gymnasium Kaliganj Karimganj held on 22<sup>nd</sup> to 24<sup>th</sup> February 2003 at Kaliganj and Secured 2<sup>nd</sup> Position in the group of 12 to 18 years age category.\n# All Barak Valley Arm-Wrestling & Yoga Best Physique Contest\u00a0 organised by Silchar Yogasan Centre held on 8<sup>th</sup> September 1996 at Silchar and secured 2<sup>nd</sup> Place in below 8 years group.\n# Rainbow Sporting Club cum Community Centre, Barak Valley Yoga Competition held on 8<sup>th</sup> February 1998 at Nilambazar College and Secured 2<sup>nd</sup> position in group \u2018A\u2019.\n# 27<sup>th</sup> All Assam Yogasan Championships 2002 Organised by Silchar Yogasan Centre & Public Health Engineering Recreation Club held at Silchar Assam and secured First position in the 8 to 12 years age group.\n# All Assam Yogasana Championship 1998 held at Silchar held from 24<sup>th</sup> to 27<sup>th</sup> December 1998 and secured First place in Nursery group category.\n# Barak Valley Power Lifting & Karimganj Dist. Yogashan Contest Organised by Ishani Club Karimganj 1997 held on 25<sup>th</sup> February 1997 at Karimganj and secured 1<sup>st</sup> place in upto 8 years age group.\n# 28<sup>th</sup> State Yoga Physique Samrat & Samragni Championship 2003 organised by Sonitpur District Body Builders Association & Sootea Sarir Sarsa Santha Dist. Sonitpur Assam and secured 1<sup>st</sup> position in the group of 12 to 18 years old.\n# All Barak Valley Arm-Wrestling & Yogasan Competition organised by Vivekananda Bayamagar,Ramkrishnanagar held on 16<sup>th</sup> February 1997 at R.K.Nagar Assam and secured 2<sup>nd</sup> position in the group of below 8 years age category.\n# Karimganj District Yoga Kumar & Yoga Kumari Championship organised by Club Martial Art. Suprakandi Karimganj Assam held on 19<sup>th</sup> April 1997 at Pailimangal High School Suprakandi and secured 1<sup>st</sup> position in the group of below 8 years age category.\n# All Barak Valley Based Competition First Anniversary of Athletic Club Bazarghat held on 5<sup>th</sup> January 1997 at Bazarghat karimganj and secured 2<sup>nd</sup> position in the group of below 8 years age.\n# Karimganj District Yogasan Championship organised by National Club, Patelnagar held on 19<sup>th</sup> January 1995 at Patelnagar Karimganj Assam and secured 1<sup>st</sup> place in the group of below 8 years age category.\n#Karimganj District Power lifting & Karimganj Town Yogashan Contest Organised by Sporting Union Club held on 6<sup>th</sup> October 1996 at Sporting Union Club Karimganj and Secured 1<sup>st</sup> place in up to 8 years yogasan age group category. \n\n=== '''<u>ARM-WRESTLING CHAMPION</u>''' ===\n\n# XXVII Senior National Arm-Wrestling Championship Organised by Arm Wrestling Association of Assam from 4<sup>th</sup> to 6<sup>th</sup> September 2003 held at B.K.B Auditorium Guwahati University Assam and secured 1<sup>st</sup> position in 50 kg weight category.\n# XXXII National Arm-wrestling Championship Organised by Chhattisgarh Arm Wrestling Association held at Nehru House of Culture Bhilai Chhattisgarh from 23<sup>rd</sup> to 27<sup>th</sup> August 2008 and Secured 1<sup>st</sup> position in 55 kg weight category.\n# XXVIII Senior National Men & Women Arm-Wrestling Championship 2004 Organised by Puri District Arm-Wrestling Association Puri held from 23<sup>rd</sup> to 25<sup>th</sup> August 2004 held at Puri Pourasadan Puri Orissa and secured 2<sup>nd</sup> position in the 50 kg weight category.\n# XXX National Arm-Wrestling Championship organised by Andhra Pradesh Arm Wrestling Association held at Lal Bahadur Indoor Stadium Hyderabad A.P. held on 25<sup>th</sup> to 27<sup>th</sup> August 2006 secured 3<sup>rd</sup> position in 55 kg weight category.\n# XXI All Barak Valley Cum N.C. Hills Arm wrestling & Yoga Championship held on 14<sup>th</sup> November 1999 at Nabin Chandra College Badarpur Assam, and secured 2<sup>nd</sup> position in the 45 kg Arm wrestling weight category.\n# Louha Krira Dibash (Kalika Prasad Dutta\u2019s Birthday Observed) Barak Valley Arm Wrestling & Karimganj District Yogasana Championship held at Karimganj High Madrassa School on 27<sup>th</sup> June 2003 and secured 1<sup>st</sup> position in the 50kg Arm Wrestling weight category.\n# Late Bhupati Chakrabarty Smriti Barak Valley Prize Money Arm-Wrestling Competition Organised by Silchar Yogasan Centre held on 20<sup>th</sup> April 2003 held at Teacher\u2019s Training College Silchar and secured 1<sup>st</sup> position in the group of 45 kg weight category.\n\n=== '''<u>INVITATION,PERFORMANCE,PARTICIPATION & DEMONSTRATION</u>''' ===\n\n# So many times, invited as a Singer, Dancer & Yoga Dancer on 15<sup>th</sup> August, 26<sup>th</sup> January and other Cultural programmes in different states.\n#Participated in 11<sup>th</sup> National Yogasan Competition Organised by Silchar Yogasan Centre held from 28<sup>th</sup> to 30<sup>th</sup> December 2005 at Silchar Assam.\n#Performed and Demonstrated Classical Song, Najurul giti,Rabindra sangeet,Patriotic Song Bihu Dance, Classical Dance, Yoga, Yoga Dance & Pyramid of Yoga on a cultural programme, Rabindrajayanti,23<sup>rd</sup> January Netaji\u2019s Birthday and other Competitions so many times in our country and that was covered by Television also.\n\n=== '''<u>ACADEMIC QUALIFICATION &PROFESSIONAL QUALIFICATION</u>''' ===\n\n* 3 years Diploma in Computer Science.\n* Bachelor of Engineering (B.E.) in Computer Science.\n* First division in Information Technology from L.B.S.T.I. DELHI.\n* Grade \u2018A\u2019 in \u2018Diploma in Computer Application\u2019 from Sterlite Foundation, Tewa Delhi.\n* Akhil Bharatiya Sangeet-O-Sanskriti Samsad (regd.) Annual Examination got 1<sup>st</sup> Division in Subject Dance held on 16<sup>th</sup> September 1993. Completed 1<sup>st</sup> year in Classical Music Examination.\n* First division in the 1<sup>st</sup> year to 6<sup>th</sup> year in Yoga examination conducted at\u00a0 Bangiya Sangeet Kala Kendra Calcutta which is Affiliated to Bhatkhande Sangeet Vidyapith (Lucknow),Akhil Bharatiya Gandharva Maha Vidyalaya Mandal (Maharashtra).\n* Participated in the workshop of Bangiya Sangeet Kala Kendra Kolkata Special Workshop On Rabindra Sangeet,Dance & Recitation Organised by Rabindradas Sangeet Mahabidyalaya held from 18<sup>th</sup> to 22<sup>nd</sup> June 2002.\n\n=== '''<u>FELICITATION,HONOR & AWARD</u>''' ===\n\n# Annual Krira Sangbadik Sangstha Award 2006-07 from BARAK UPATYAKA KRIRA SANGBADIK SANGSTHA for Best Arm Wrestler held on 11<sup>th</sup> April 2008 in Silchar Assam.\n# 4<sup>th</sup> North East Yoga Competition best position holder felicitation given by Karimganj District Yoga Physique Association held on 9<sup>th</sup> March 2003 at Youth Unity Club Karimganj Assam.\n# 59<sup>th</sup> Independence Day on 15<sup>th</sup> August 2005 from Government for best Player in Arm Sports.\n# 11<sup>th</sup> Assam Sports & Cultural Festival & Louho Purush Premodakanta 92th Birthday Celebration held at Guwahati on 22<sup>nd</sup> December 2006.<br />\n", "text_old": "{{db-person|help=off}}\nShe is only child of Mr. Kalika Prasad Dutta and Pradipta Dutta ,Born In 4th October 1989 Silchar Assam.\n\nShe started Her Sports Career At the age of 3 Years ,its  unbelievable Dancing, Yoga, and Study ,She did Perfectly.\n\nhere is some achievements of her  \n\n== PROFESSIONAL & OTHER SPECIAL ACTIVITIES ==\n\n* Teacher of Yoga dance in M.K YOGA DANCE College\n* Singer in JHANKAR SHILPI SANSTHA..\n* National,State & Barak Valley Level Champion in Arm-Wrestling & Yoga.\n* Represented India in the XVIII World Arm-Wrestling Championship in MANCHESTER, ENGLAND in the year 2006 & secured 4<sup>th</sup> position in the 50 kg weight categ